Very genuine?

872
00:38:05,540 --> 00:38:07,420
So do you live alone now,

873
00:38:07,420 --> 00:38:08,740
or with your parents?

874
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:10,300
I've always lived alone.

875
00:38:11,180 --> 00:38:12,300
My parents passed away early.

876
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:13,860
Later, I had some luck.

877
00:38:13,860 --> 00:38:14,860
Started some businesses

878
00:38:14,860 --> 00:38:15,860
and made some money.

879
00:38:16,180 --> 00:38:17,980
I also made some friends in real estate.

880
00:38:18,540 --> 00:38:20,460
Now we have an investment company.

881
00:38:21,060 --> 00:38:21,820
If I said I'm a fairy,

882
00:38:21,820 --> 00:38:22,420
would you believe me?

883
00:38:22,540 --> 00:38:23,180
I'd believe it.

884
00:38:23,940 --> 00:38:25,860
Were you single when you descended?

885
00:38:26,660 --> 00:38:28,420
How do you know I'm single?

886
00:38:29,980 --> 00:38:32,300
The whole world
heard you shouting about it that day.

887
00:38:37,020 --> 00:38:37,660
Then

888
00:38:38,820 --> 00:38:39,380
what about you?

889
00:38:41,220 --> 00:38:42,460
I haven't been
in a relationship for years.

890
00:38:44,020 --> 00:38:45,300
Never met the right person.

891
00:38:47,540 --> 00:38:49,180
Love is something

892
00:38:50,020 --> 00:38:51,060
you can't force.

893
00:38:51,940 --> 00:38:52,700
Just go with the flow.

894
00:38:54,860 --> 00:38:56,180
But I still envy those

895
00:38:56,180 --> 00:38:57,100
who have love.

896
00:39:00,220 --> 00:39:00,980
I just feel like

897
00:39:00,980 --> 00:39:02,780
love isn't in the cards for me.

898
00:39:03,740 --> 00:39:05,420
My past relationships...

899
00:39:10,260 --> 00:39:11,060
You got hurt?

900
00:39:14,700 --> 00:39:15,940
Actually, I don't think

901
00:39:16,940 --> 00:39:18,620
love itself hurts people.

902
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:21,420
What hurts us is probably

903
00:39:22,300 --> 00:39:23,420
the person within that love.

904
00:39:23,900 --> 00:39:24,620
But when we meet

905
00:39:24,620 --> 00:39:25,820
the right person,

906
00:39:26,620 --> 00:39:27,820
then love can be good.

907
00:39:33,980 --> 00:39:34,820
You're right, Mr. Wu.

908
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:36,820
Don't call me Mr. Wu.

909
00:39:36,900 --> 00:39:38,180
Makes it sound like
we're doing business.

910
00:39:38,460 --> 00:39:38,940
Call me Zu.

911
00:39:40,620 --> 00:39:41,140
Zu.

912
00:39:49,140 --> 00:39:49,820
Cheers.

913
00:40:17,860 --> 00:40:18,260
Here.

914
