Take it slow.

915
00:40:28,700 --> 00:40:29,580
You should head back now.

916
00:40:31,260 --> 00:40:31,860
I'm going.

917
00:40:38,380 --> 00:40:38,740
Bye.

918
00:40:39,260 --> 00:40:39,580
Bye.

919
00:40:40,540 --> 00:40:41,020
Let's go, sir.

