934
00:41:28,620 --> 00:41:29,740
I... I'll deliver the food.

935
00:41:29,900 --> 00:41:31,460
Okay. Bye.

936
00:41:31,740 --> 00:41:32,300
Does it hurt?

937
00:41:32,340 --> 00:41:32,700
No.

938
00:41:33,980 --> 00:41:34,900
Lift it up a bit.

939
00:41:35,660 --> 00:41:35,860
Okay.

940
00:41:36,300 --> 00:41:36,820
Tighten it a bit more.

941
00:41:37,420 --> 00:41:37,940
Okay.

942
00:41:38,180 --> 00:41:38,740
How is it, doctor?

943
00:41:39,220 --> 00:41:39,780
Not bad.

944
00:42:04,940 --> 00:42:05,460
Wang Shuhan.

945
