950
00:42:31,420 --> 00:42:32,340
Solo concert.

951
00:42:32,820 --> 00:42:33,780
Wedding invitation.

952
00:42:34,780 --> 00:42:36,260
Look how happy Ms. Wen is now.

953
00:42:36,380 --> 00:42:37,980
Successful in both career and love.

954
00:42:38,380 --> 00:42:38,900
Ms. Wen,

955
00:42:38,980 --> 00:42:40,660
