to your wedding.

956
00:42:41,060 --> 00:42:41,660
Of course I will.

957
00:42:41,660 --> 00:42:43,180
How could I forget you all?

958
00:42:43,860 --> 00:42:45,060
Ms. Wen,

959
00:42:45,580 --> 00:42:47,580
